==English==

===Etymology===
From the nickname of [[tweak]] for methamphetamines, in reference to addicts' [[w:punding|punding]] behavior.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# {{slang}} A person addicted to [[methamphetamine]]s.
# A tool for making small adjustments.
# A person who makes small adjustments using a tweaker (2).

